atrik Koy\u0161|P. Koy\u0161]] (M. R\u00e9way) (ENG)\n| attendance = 13,625\n| stadium = [[Air Canada Centre]]\n| official = {{flagicon|RUS}} Roman Gofman\n| official2 = {{flagicon|RUS}} Konstantin Olenin\n| linesman = {{flagicon|CAN}} Bevan Mills\n| linesman2 = {{flagicon|USA}} Judson Ritter\n| reference = http://stats.iihf.com/Hydra/417/IHM417130_74_4_0.pdf\n| penalties1 = 29\n| penalties2 = 6\n| shots1 = 28\n| shots2 = 28\n}}\n\n====Final====\n{{IceHockeybox\n| bg = #F7F6A8\n| date = January 5, 2015\n| time = 20:00\n| team1 = '''{{ihj-rt|CAN}}'''\n| score =  5\u20134\n| team2 = {{ihj|RUS}}\n| progression = 1\u20130<br>2\u20130<br>2\u20131<br>3\u20131<br>4\u20131<br>5\u20131<br>5\u20132<br>5\u20133<br>5\u20134\n| periods = (2\u20131, 3\u20133, 0\u20130)\n| goalie1 = [[Zachary Fucale]]\n| goalie2 = [[Igor Shestyorkin]]<br>[[Ilya Sorokin]]\n| goals1 = [[Anthony Duclair|A. Duclair]] ([[Max Domi|M. Domi]]) \u2013 00:23<br>[[Nick Paul|N. Paul]] ([[Brayden Point|B. Point]], [[Jake Virtanen|J. Virtanen]]) \u2013 02:32<br><br>[[Connor McDavid|C. McDavid]] ([[Josh Morrissey|J. Morrissey]]) \u2013 25:08<br>M. Domi \u2013 27:22<br>M. Domi ([[Sam Reinhart|S. Reinhart]]) \u2013 32:30\n| goals2 = <br><br>09:20 \u2013 [[Dmitry Yudin|D. Yudin]] ([[Anatoli Golyshev|A. Golyshev]], [[Alexander Dergachyov|A. Dergachyov]])<br><br><br><br>34:21 \u2013 [[Ivan Barbashev|I. Barbashev]] ([[Pavel Buchnevich|P. Buchnevich]], D. Yudin) (PP)<br>34:53 \u2013 [[Sergei Tolchinski|S. Tolchinski]] ([[Nikolay Goldobin|N. Goldobin]], [[Rinat Valiev|R. Valiev]])<br>37:37 \u2013 N. Goldobin (S. Tolchinski, [[Vladislav Kanenev|V. Kamenev]]) (PP)\n| attendance = 19,014\n| stadium = [[Air Canada Centre]]\n| official = {{flagicon|SWE}} Marcus Vinnerborg\n| official2 = {{flagicon|SUI}} Tobias Wehrli\n| linesman = {{flagicon|CZE}} Miroslav Lhotsk\u00fd\n| linesman2 = {{flagicon|SWE}} Andreas Malmqvist\n| reference = http://stats.iihf.com/Hydra/417/IHM417131_74_3_0.pdf\n| penalties1 = 8\n| penalties2 = 22\n| 