31_74_3_0.pdf\n| penalties1 = 8\n| penalties2 = 22\n| shots1 = 21\n| shots2 = 30\n}}\n\n=== Statistics ===\n\n==== Scoring leaders ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!width=30|Pos\n!width=150|Player\n!width=120|Country\n!width=20|GP\n!width=20|G\n!width=20|A\n!width=30|Pts\n!width=30|+/\u2212\n!width=30|PIM\n|-\n| 1 || align=left|[[Sam Reinhart]] || align=left|{{ihj|CAN}} || 7 || 5 || 6 || '''11''' || +13 || 6\n|-\n| 2 || align=left|[[Nic Petan]] || align=left|{{ihj|CAN}} || 7 || 4 || 7 || '''11''' || +4 || 0\n|-\n| 3 || align=left|[[Connor McDavid]] || align=left|{{ihj|CAN}} || 7 || 3 || 8 || '''11''' || +8 || 0\n|-\n| 4 || align=left|[[Max Domi]] || align=left|{{ihj|CAN}} || 7 || 5 || 5 || '''10''' || +10 || 4\n|-\n| 5 || align=left|[[William Nylander]] || align=left|{{ihj|SWE}} || 7 || 3 || 7 || '''10''' || \u20132 || 0\n|-\n| 6 || align=left|[[Curtis Lazar]] || align=left|{{ihj|CAN}} || 7 || 5 || 4 || '''9''' || +8 || 0\n|-\n| 7 || align=left|[[Oskar Lindblom]] || align=left|{{ihj|SWE}} || 7 || 4 || 5 || '''9''' || \u20131 || 0\n|-\n| 7 || align=left|[[Martin R\u00e9way]] || align=left|{{ihj|SVK}} || 7 || 4 || 5 || '''9''' || \u20131 || 2\n|-\n| 9 || align=left|[[Adrian Kempe]] || align=left|{{ihj|SWE}} || 6 || 4 || 4 || '''8''' || 0 || 2\n|-\n| 10 || align=left|[[Anthony Duclair]] || align=left|{{ihj|CAN}} || 7 || 4 || 4 || '''8''' || +11 || 16\n|-\n\n|}<small>''GP = Games played; G = Goals; A = Assists; Pts = Points; +/\u2212 = [[Plus-minus]]; PIM = Penalties In Minutes''\nSource: [http://stats.iihf.com/Hydra/417/IHM417000_85B_10_0.pdf IIHF.com]</small>\n\n==== Goaltending leaders ====\n(minimum 40% team's total ice time)\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!width=30|Pos\n!width=150|Player\n!width=120|Country\n!width=20|TOI\n!width=20|GA\n!width=20|GAA\n!width=20|Sv%\n!width=20|SO\n|-\n| 1 || align=left|[[Zachary Fucale]] || align=left|{{ihj|CAN}} || 300:00 || 6 || 1.20 || 93.94 || 2\n|-\n